    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade masterpiece that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, shielded from the elements since its first mile. The exterior paint is absolutely flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish enhanced by a multi-stage paint correction and professional ceramic coating; you will find zero rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Step inside to an interior that remains in showroom state\u2014the premium leather upholstery is supple with no bolster wear or creasing, the carpets are protected by original factory mats, and the cabin retains its original factory scent. Every electronic component, from the infotainment system to the smallest ambient light, functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a folder of exhaustive service records performed exclusively by master technicians. The engine bay is immaculate, showing no signs of dust or fluid seepage. This sale includes two sets of keys, the original window sticker, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a bespoke indoor car cover. For the buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this is the one.",
